Moulkiwtis Grigorios
1115201900117

Sxediastikes epiloges einai gnwsto pws to megisto filename sta linux einai 4096 xaraktires to opoio kai xrisimopoiithike.
Xrisimopoiithikan oi domes tis stl map kai queue.
Yparxei Makefile gia tin metaglwttisi kai ektelesi tou programmatos.
Kathe worker mporei na epeksergazetai diaforetika arxeia ean einai diathesimos.
Parexontai sxolia se kathe arxeio.
Gia kapoion logo i inotify den epistrefei ola ta arxeia otan eisagwntai ola mazi.
I stl dimiourgei leaks.
Ta .out arxeia vriskontai ena epipedo panw apo to ektelesimo.
To valgring dyskoleyetai na vgalei apotelesmata otan trexoume ta arxeia twn test alla genika to programma den exei leaks.

Metaglwttisi:
make compile
Ektelesi: 
./sniffer [-p path]

Epeksigisi kwdika:
main:
Elegxos orismatwn kai dimiougia pipe.THesimo tou Ctrl-C se termatismo,proetimasia twn orismatwn tis inotifywait.Fork gia tin dimiourgia tou listener kai fork-exec gia tin dimiourgia tis inotify.O Manager analamvanei ton elegxo.Molis lavoume arxeio dimiougia worker ean den yparxei diathesimos alliws ksypnima idi yparxonta kai parsing tou arxeiou.
end:
Skotwma diergasiwn kai apeleftherwsi mnimis.
worker:
Parsing kai apothikefsi dedomenwn sta arxeia,epipleon stamatima tou worker.
